Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.97,0:00:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见会记住我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.31,0:00:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕会这样慢慢习惯战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.07,0:00:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得自己好像会变成另一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.10,0:00:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实大家都怀着不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.67,0:00:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许没有人可以毫无改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.23,0:00:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们确实在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.91,0:00:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会记着一骑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.10,0:00:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在放弃还来得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  到外面的世界去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就行了  这样就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.85,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11话  旧新～人类军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见一骑那家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷在阿尔比斯里变成罐头了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.73,0:03:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻说  一骑和狩谷老师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩是那种关系？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被允许的爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年龄相差悬殊的二人选择的道路是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私·奔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害厉害厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.61,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么潇洒的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙只是因为害怕才逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是临阵脱逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临阵脱逃的话会有什么后果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.91,0:04:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了蠢事啊  由纪惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.75,0:04:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.41,0:04:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾生活着几十亿人的世界的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.41,0:05:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士看到过了吧  这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要降落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你操纵得很熟练啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是恭维吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我没这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.41,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是法弗尼尔的驾驶员候选啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于精灵号驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连合作用的形成率与精神状态都没有任何问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.72,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能认为是外部诱因造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.66,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩谷由纪惠这个外部诱因吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于真壁一骑和狩谷由纪惠的处置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能交给我来办吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.11,0:06:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩谷由纪惠是新国联的间谍这件事\N我和皆城公藏都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.51,0:06:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在弄清她的目的之前原本不想轻举妄动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.28,0:06:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果造成这种事都是我的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.79,0:07:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被小姑娘打了个措手不及该适可而止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.15,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想到连你儿子也赔上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这也是道弘的计策吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.87,0:07:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了他还有谁会想出这种招数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.61,0:07:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  现在开始是最糟的局面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是你  已经下定决心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.43,0:07:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你在后悔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得如果那样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.51,0:08:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会变成另一个自己  所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.81,0:08:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那个岛不是你应该待的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.86,0:08:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你不应该保护岛屿而希望你能保护世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.28,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护世界  我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的法弗尼尔驾驶员是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.51,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用这个能打败菲斯特姆我会不惜一切代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.27,0:08:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人也说过\N必须了解制造法弗尼尔的真正意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.63,0:08:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让岛上的那些人明白  真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.60,0:08:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  「那个人」是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.71,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.36,0:09:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会被发现的  必须快点离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能离开这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟它战斗  真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.36,0:09:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不起作用？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.23,0:10:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  打倒它  真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁  回到地面待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.99,0:10:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是法弗尼尔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没什么嚼头啊  这个斯芬克司型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.44,0:11:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRIBBLE6号  目标的同化确认完成了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我哪知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.34,0:11:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加侬  这是我的猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.55,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行  因为是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺顿模型发射确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经听腻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.69,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差得远呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜  被他赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经在那里  现在已不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起枪口的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.73,0:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨着那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剥开衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.07,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬下她的皮肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后将她毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.37,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  那法弗尼尔究竟是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自己人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  好快的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说  不说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.82,0:13:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我们添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加侬  不是叫你别出手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.88,0:13:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么赔我的乐趣来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务优先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令说游戏是那之后的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一个古板的家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走  上船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到驾驶员是一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着加侬  这是上司的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次等我游戏结束之后再考虑任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会与规则矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个脑子不灵活的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真迟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于还不一定会来的人应该避免使用战力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  由纪惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是道生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分  现在才发觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.82,0:15:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲  诺顿模型也变成了这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.60,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗了我  你的目的是法弗尼尔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.81,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会按照约定带你去乐园的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么乐园  我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.94,0:16:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少现在要去的地方  对我来说就是乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.21,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  你先忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满意了吗  由纪惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子还太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.40,0:16:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和皆城公蔵太过亲密的事这里也调查到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.98,0:16:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在怀疑你是不是反间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是任务  别怪我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.16,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的事告诉那个人  他一定会改变想法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生你听见没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日野道生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.19,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点吵  那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.41,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我过去在岛上时相比变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.49,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是不肯安静  就拿东西堵住她的嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得到诺顿模型了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.87,0:17:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我代表全世界感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.68,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特兰德博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.83,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样阿卡迪尔计划也会对人类有所贡献了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.34,0:18:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有补充这两人才能保住岛屿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.31,0:18:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔已经准备完成的报告也收到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.21,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不单是一骑  连这两人也被卷进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.28,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人…不  都是我的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事不是你的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道弘所做过的事  都是经过精心计算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用法弗尼尔可以改变世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.57,0:18:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那个人到现在也这么深信着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.55,0:18:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了战胜菲斯特姆  道弘抛弃了龙宫岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有值得保护的东西  战斗是无意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.51,0:19:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛上第一个灵魂被法弗尼尔同化的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.95,0:19:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有点累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校的活动计划表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业典礼也有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.46,0:19:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一定要办的吧  一般说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于一骑的事听说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.41,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见会记住我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.86,0:20:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑  你现在在哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.14,0:20:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑离岛之前  最后和你谈过话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑说了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说想逃避战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.72,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说想逃避我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.86,0:20:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  他只说希望别人能记住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想问一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑对皆城说了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  什么也没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说他是逃跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.65,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一骑多谈一谈不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逃避的是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.21,0:21:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.96,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…如果是那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.93,0:21:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为他能理解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.87,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一定是这么想的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.95,0:21:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经多少次拥有相同的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.24,0:22:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连痛苦和创伤也是同一羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.25,0:22:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  太希望对方了解自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而忘了对方就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.99,0:22:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做才能回到过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.47,0:22:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无从知晓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.01,0:23:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强迫战斗的孩子们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.14,0:23:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能注视着的大人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.33,0:23:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在  他不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.99,0:23:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  苍穹的Fafnir  第十二话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.49,0:23:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.97,0:23:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗


